From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Kurt Miller <bsdkurt@gmail.com>
Date: Mon, 16 Feb 2026 19:17:42 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] 8981: Add OpenBSD support for x86_64 and arm_64.

Add OpenBSD support for x86_64 and arm_64.

Use installed protobuf package for protoc on OpenBSD

Fix gdb on OpenBSD/amd64 by: * Filtering out registers that are "<unavailable>" when querying gdb for register list. * Force querying gdb for register list on OpenBSD.
